en_485179_0	Major General C J Abayaratna (Retd) of Sri Lanka Signal Corps (SLSC) who was the first Colonel Commandant of the SLSC Regiment passed away on Sunday (9).
en_485179_1	His funeral with military honours takes place on Tuesday (11) at the General Cemetery, Borella at 4.00 p.m.
en_485179_2	His remains are lying at A.F Raymond Funeral Parlour, Colombo.
